Subject: Hardcode GDB python module directory

Forwarded: not-needed

Debian package installs python modules into a fixed directory, so
just hardcode path in wrapper script.
---
 src/etc/rust-gdb    | 2 +-
 src/etc/rust-gdbgui | 2 +-
